                            Framework</h5>
                        <p>Open source web application framework for ASP.NET Core that provides a complete infrastructure to create modern web applications by following software development best practices and conventions.</p>
                        <a href="https://abp.io/features" target="_blank"
                            class="btn btn-link px-1">Features <i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i></a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-4 border-left">
                    <div class="p-4">
